Package javax.constraints.extra

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Propagator
    This interface represents propagators that used to propagate PropagationEvents when new(!) custom constraints are defined.
    Reversible
    This interface represents reversible integers.
    ReversibleAction
    This interface represents application-specific actions that can be added during the search and executed during backtracking.
